Flask-Anyform Changelog
=======================

Here you can see the full list of changes between each Flask-Anyform release.

Version 0.0.2
-------------

Released September 27th 2013

- removal of post-init adding of forms
- collapse adding of context function to one decorator (form_ctx)
- cleanup overall and in testing


Version 0.0.1
-------------

Released September 23th 2013

- initial release



